data.description: Endless Gulf Views at this spacious, custom-built home on tranquil No Name Key, a small coastal island offering abundant privacy, higher elevation, and incomparable deep draft boating, just 30 miles from exciting Key West! This renovated home boasts a bright and airy 1,724 sq. ft. floorplan with impact doors and windows, and a well-equipped kitchen featuring sleek granite countertops, large island with seating, and stainless-steel appliances. Low-maintenance engineered hardwood flooring provides warmth and character throughout the space. The open-concept floorplan lends itself to entertaining, with an expansive upstairs loft offering stunning Open Water and Canal Views. Enjoy morning coffee or evening cocktails with friends from either of two upstairs screened-in balconies or open wrap-around decks, with views of the turquoise waters of the Gulf. Fish for snapper and tarpon right from the back yard with approximately 35 feet of composite dockage, enhanced with 50, 30, and 15 amp service, and located on a 60' wide sailboat canal with easy Gulf and Ocean access. Offering an abundance of covered parking with a spacious garage, and additional open parking for RV and trailer storage. Fully outfitted for comfort no matter the weather, this home is equipped with a whole-home generator and 17,000 gallon cistern. Nestled on a peaceful, picturesque island, surrounded by nature, the ultimate Keys lifestyle awaits. Schedule a tour today!
